Location
Preservation Point is located in the Heart of Florida’s nature coast! The private resort is accessed from U.S. Hwy. 44 (a divided 4 lane highway) just two miles east of Inverness, FL and is surrounded by beautiful
Lake Tsala Apopka
. The short drive is only 12 miles away from Interstate-75 and the Florida Turnpike. The “Wildwood Truck Stop” exit on I-75 has extensive RV Service and repair facilities. Our resort is only one hour away from Disney World and other Orlando theme parks.
